<concept id="cgsinstr" xml:lang="en-us">
<title>System requirements</title>
<shortdesc><ph conref="../conrefs.dita#prod/productshortname"></ph> is a database
engine written completely in the Java programming language. The database will run in any certified
Java Virtual Machine (JVM).</shortdesc>
<conbody>
<p>You must have a Java Development Kit (JDK) version 1.4 or higher installed on your computer.
The JDK is required to perform the activities in the <xref
href="cgstutorialintro.dita#cgstutorialintro"></xref>. </p>
<p>To check that the correct version of the JDK is installed, issue the <codeph>java
-version</codeph> command.</p>
</conbody>
</concept>
